# DnD Companion — Frontend Routes

Tüm route tanımları `routes/index.tsx` (veya `App.tsx` router config) merkezinde. React Router v6 data/nested layout pattern. Path'ler kebab-case İngilizce.

Genel mimari → `20-frontend-general.mdc`; form sayfaları → `22-frontend-forms.mdc`.

## Route Organizasyonu

```
routes/index.tsx     # createBrowserRouter veya <Routes> ağacı
layouts/             # PublicLayout, AppLayout, AdminLayout
pages/               # Route-level default export
features/auth/       # AuthGuard, AdminGuard
```

Sayfa bileşeni `pages/<domain>/<Name>Page.tsx`; route path ile dosya adı tutarlı (`CampaignDetailPage` → `/campaigns/:id`).

## Layout Nesting

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — nested layout + guard
{
  element: <AuthGuard><AppLayout /></AuthGuard>,
  children: [
    { path: '/campaigns', element: <CampaignListPage /> },
    { path: '/campaigns/:id/dm-screen', element: <DmScreenPage /> },
  ],
},
{
  element: <PublicLayout />,
  children: [
    { path: '/login', element: <LoginPage /> },
    { path: '/homebrew', element: <HomebrewGalleryPage /> },
  ],
},
{
  element: <AuthGuard><AdminGuard><AdminLayout /></AdminGuard></AuthGuard>,
  children: [
    { path: '/admin/users', element: <AdminUsersPage /> },
  ],
}

// ✗ Yanlış — her sayfada layout tekrarı
function CampaignListPage() {
  return <AppLayout><Content /></AppLayout>;
}
```

## Auth Seviyeleri (UX)

| Sembol | Anlam | Guard |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Public | Misafir erişir | Yok |
| App | Giriş zorunlu | `AuthGuard` |
| Mixed | Kaynağa göre (public character) | Sayfa içi API + koşullu layout |
| Admin | `role === ADMIN` | `AuthGuard` + `AdminGuard` |

**Kritik:** Guard'lar yalnızca UX — backend her istekte JWT + policy doğrular. Yetkisiz kullanıcı guard'ı bypass etse bile API `403`/`404` döner.

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — AuthGuard UX
function AuthGuard({ children }: { children: React.ReactNode }) {
  const { user, isLoading } = useAuth();
  if (isLoading) return <LoadingSpinner />;
  if (!user) return <Navigate to="/login" replace state={{ from: location }} />;
  return <>{children}</>;
}

// ✗ Yanlış — guard'ta yetki kararı (DM mi?)
if (campaign.ownerId !== user.id) throw new Error('Forbidden');
```

## Email Doğrulama UX

`EmailVerificationBanner` layout'ta — route **bloklamaz**. Yazma sayfalarında butonlar `disabled` + tooltip: `"Please verify your email to perform this action"`. API `403 EMAIL_NOT_VERIFIED` yedek.

## Route Path Konvansiyonu

| Pattern | Örnek |
| --- | --- |
| Liste | `/campaigns`, `/characters` |
| Oluştur | `/campaigns/new`, `/characters/new` |
| Detay | `/campaigns/:id`, `/characters/:id` |
| Düzenle | `/campaigns/:id/edit` |
| Alt özellik | `/campaigns/:id/dm-screen` |
| Public galeri | `/homebrew`, `/reference/:type` |
| Token query | `/verify-email?token=`, `/reset-password/confirm?token=` |
| Catch-all | `*` → `NotFoundPage` |

Tam path listesi → `docs/05_FRONTEND_SPEC.md` Bölüm 2. Ekran ID eşlemesi → `docs/06_SCREEN_CATALOG.md` Bölüm 1 (`S-*`).

Route path ile katalog ID çelişirse **docs/05 routing + 06 ID** birlikte okunur; implementasyonda 05 path öncelikli, ID sabit kalır.

## createBrowserRouter İskeleti

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — merkezi router config
export const router = createBrowserRouter([
  {
    element: <PublicLayout />,
    children: [
      { path: '/login', element: <LoginPage /> },
      { path: '/homebrew', element: <HomebrewGalleryPage /> },
      { path: '/reference/:type?/:id?', element: <ReferenceRoutes /> },
    ],
  },
  {
    element: (
      <AuthGuard>
        <AppLayout />
      </AuthGuard>
    ),
    children: [
      { index: true, element: <Navigate to="/campaigns" replace /> },
      { path: '/campaigns', element: <CampaignListPage /> },
      {
        path: '/campaigns/:id/dm-screen',
        element: (
          <Suspense fallback={<LoadingSpinner />}>
            <DmScreenPage />
          </Suspense>
        ),
      },
    ],
  },
  { path: '*', element: <NotFoundPage /> },
]);
```

## Ekran ID (S-*) Kullanımı

Yeni veya değişen sayfada katalog ID'sini koru:

| ID | Route (spec) | Page dosyası |
| --- | --- | --- |
| S-LOGIN | `/login` | `LoginPage.tsx` |
| S-DM-SCREEN | `/campaigns/:id/dm-screen` | `DmScreenPage.tsx` |
| S-CHAR-BUILDER | `/characters/new` | `CharacterBuilderPage.tsx` |
| S-HOMEBREW-GALLERY | `/homebrew` | `HomebrewGalleryPage.tsx` |
| S-ADMIN-USERS | `/admin/users` | `AdminUsersPage.tsx` |

Alan/state tablosu katalogda kalır — rule'da tekrarlanmaz. Yeni ekran prosedürü → `41-add-new-screen`.

## Lazy Loading (Zorunlu)

Ağır sayfalar code-split:

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru
const DmScreenPage = lazy(() => import('../pages/dm-screen/DmScreenPage'));
const CharacterBuilderPage = lazy(() => import('../pages/characters/CharacterBuilderPage'));
const AdminUsersPage = lazy(() => import('../pages/admin/AdminUsersPage'));

<Route
  path="/campaigns/:id/dm-screen"
  element={
    <Suspense fallback={<LoadingSpinner />}>
      <DmScreenPage />
    </Suspense>
  }
/>

// ✗ Yanlış — admin/ builder static import (bundle şişer)
import { DmScreenPage } from './pages/dm-screen/DmScreenPage';
```

Zorunlu lazy: tüm `/admin/*`, `CharacterBuilderPage`, `DmScreenPage`, `CharacterEditPage` (multi-tab).

## Dinamik Document Title

Her route `useEffect` veya layout helper ile `<title>` günceller — İngilizce:

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru
usePageTitle('My Campaigns — DnD Companion');
usePageTitle(campaign ? `${campaign.name} — DnD Companion` : 'Campaign — DnD Companion');

// ✗ Yanlış — statik index.html title veya Türkçe
<title>Kampanyalarım</title>
```

404/500 sayfaları: `"Page Not Found — DnD Companion"`, `"Server Error — DnD Companion"`.

## Mixed Auth Sayfaları

`CharacterDetailPage`, `HomebrewDetailPage`: public kaynak misafire açık; layout Public veya App seçimi API response'a göre.

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — API sonrası render; hata 404
const { data, isLoading, error } = useGetCharacterQuery(id);
if (isLoading) return <LoadingSpinner />;
if (error) return <NotFoundPage />;
// Public character: PublicLayout wrapper veya read-only sheet
```

Frontend'de `visibility === 'PUBLIC'` ile erken karar verme — API yetkisizde `404` döner.

## Redirect ve Navigasyon

| Durum | Hedef |
| --- | --- |
| `/` (auth) | `/campaigns` |
| Login başarı | `location.state.from` veya `/campaigns` |
| Logout | `/login` |
| Admin değil `/admin/*` | `/` (`AdminGuard`) |
| Geçersiz invite token | hata state + `/campaigns` |

`Navigate` ile `replace` tercih et (login loop önleme).

## Query Parametreleri

Token tabanlı auth sayfaları query kullanır (`?token=`). `useSearchParams` ile oku; token yoksa inline error + link home.

Path param UUID: route `/:id` — geçersiz format backend `400`; sayfa loading → error state.

## Invite Route

`/invite/:token` — auth zorunlu. Token path'te; join mutation sonrası `/campaigns/:id`. Invalid token → toast + campaign list.

## Breadcrumb

App layout header'da dinamik breadcrumb (`nav aria-label="Breadcrumb"`). Detay → `25-frontend-a11y.mdc`.

## Oturum Restore ve Router

`App.tsx`: refresh tamamlanmadan `<RouterProvider>` mount etme — flash redirect önlenir.

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru sıra
if (isInitializing) return <LoadingSpinner fullScreen />;
return <RouterProvider router={router} />;
```

## Session Expired Modal (S-SESSION-EXPIRED)

Overlay route değil — global modal. Refresh başarısız + korumalı sayfada işlem:

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — modal kapatılamaz
<Dialog open={sessionExpired} onOpenChange={() => {}}>
  <DialogContent hideCloseButton role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
    <DialogTitle>Session expired</DialogTitle>
    <p>Please sign in again to continue.</p>
    <Button onClick={() => navigate('/login')}>Sign in</Button>
  </DialogContent>
</Dialog>
```

`Escape` devre dışı — `25-frontend-a11y.mdc` istisna.

## Error Boundary ve 404/500

- `NotFoundPage` (S-404): catch-all `*` route, Public layout.
- `ServerErrorPage` (S-500): React error boundary fallback; retry + home link.
- Boundary admin/app ağacına yakın — tek sayfa crash tüm app'i öldürmez.

## Sidebar Nav Öğeleri (App)

Campaigns, Characters, Reference, Homebrew Gallery, My Creations, My Collection, Profile. Admin kullanıcıda dropdown veya sidebar alt bölüm: Admin Panel → `/admin/users`.

Nav link `NavLink` + `aria-current="page"` aktif route'ta.

## Reference Route Parametreleri

`/reference` — tüm tipler. `/reference/:type` — filtreli liste. `/reference/:type/:id` — detay. Public layout; auth opsiyonel.

